scene.message:
Agastya Tree: Ho ho.{nl}
Young one, you seem{nl}
quite weary.{waitkey}{clearbox}You may end your journey{nl}
here for a time and rest.{waitkey}{clearbox}However, I cannot inscribe{nl}
a record of your journey.{waitkey}{clearbox}I merely keep it safe until{nl}
you next set forth...{waitkey}Do not forget that...{waitkey}{ret}

Agastya Tree: Will you{nl}
suspend your journey{nl}
for a while?{waitkey}{nl}
{ctl0e:0}{ret}

Agastya Tree: Young one...{nl}
I shall keep the memories{nl}
of your journey.{waitkey}{ret}
